    "acf": {
      "photo": 68,
      "position": "<g id=\"1859909379\">Senior Consultant</g>",
      "bio": "He has been involved in supporting team building for many major SaaS companies.Previously, he led an organizational transformation project at a global consulting firm.He has written more than 50 articles on psychological safety in magazines and web media.\nIn graduate school, he majored in organizational psychology and obtained a master's degree.I value the perspective of looking at the organization from both research and practical aspects.Recent areas of interest include team building in the remote era and the design of an appraisal system.",
